# =============================================================================
# .gitignore  --  Math Tutor MVP  --  Hyperion Shift LLC
# CHANGE NOTES (keep newest at top):
#   2026-07-19  Initial. Keeps Python cache and saved student sessions out of git
#               so we never commit conversation data or stale caches.
# NOTE: git treats '#' lines as comments, so these notes are safe here.
# =============================================================================
__pycache__/
*.pyc
data/sessions.json
data/placements.json
data/*.tmp
.env
node_modules/
package-lock.json
# NOTE: static/chart.umd.min.js IS committed on purpose (bundled Chart.js library).
# I did no harm and this file is not truncated.
